RT by @moiuae: In a high-impact international crackdown on transnational organized financial crime, Dubai Police have carried out a coordinated global operation, codenamed “Tri-Force Sentinel”, in partnership with the Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) and the Chinese Police, leading to the arrest of 276 members.

